description: GAD-7 form that is intended for IPC Session 1

item.text: A place to declare values that cannot be created using FHIRPath such as Coding. Retrieve the following items has answer value using variable expression, to use the declared value.
Observation ID of GAD-7 Session 1 Score
The next seven questions are from the Generalized Anxiety Disorder-7. These questions measure anxiety.
Over the last 2 weeks, how often have you been bothered by the following problems?

extension.valueString: Durante as últimas 2 semanas, com que frequência você se sentiu incomodado(a) por qualquer um dos síntomas abaixo?

item.text:
Tip #1
List symptoms, describe severity (what the summed up scores mean), and impact on daily activities.

Tip #2
Please see severity levels for the GAD-7
• 0-4 = Minimal anxiety
• 5-9 = Mild anxiety
• 10-14 = Moderate anxiety
• 15+ = Severe anxiety
Suggested anxiety severity based on GAD-7 score
